{"TopicId":185157,"ForumId":69,"TopicTitle":"Any body know how to fix lag when in vicinity of Kerbin?","CreatedByName":"astrospacedude","CreatedById":197923,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-06-05T00:28:57Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"astrospacedude","CreatedById":197923,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-06-05T00:28:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi, when in the vicinity of Kerbin it lags, and to stop it i have to look at the sky, does anybody know how to fix\u00A0 it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-06-05T00:46:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEver since I started playing, around v .18, I\u0027ve had to turn the camera away from the planet to get better frame rates.\u00A0\u00A0 I think it has to do with the rendering of the water.\u00A0\u00A0 So yeah, during launch, camera is facing up, and during orbit, facing out.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"astrospacedude","CreatedById":197923,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-06-05T06:38:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nApparently there was a fix at this link (\u003Ca href=\u0022https://kerbalspaceprogram.com/forum/index.php?topic=13682.0\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Ehttps://kerbalspaceprogram.com/forum/index.php?topic=13682.0\u003C/a\u003E) but it doesn\u0027t exist anymore.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"GearsNSuch","CreatedById":190371,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-06-05T10:07:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/197923-astrospacedude/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022197923\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/197923-astrospacedude/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@astrospacedude\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI may be wrong, but I believe the Kopernicus mod will fix that to some degree.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think they incorporated the fix you linked a little while ago.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed8158721490\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/181547-170-1-backports-kopernicus-kittopiatech/\u0026amp;tab=comments\u0026amp;do=embed\u0026amp;comment=2602496\u0026amp;embedComment=2602496\u0026amp;embedDo=findComment#comment-2602496\u0022 style=\u0022height:309px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEnjoy!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-06-05T10:07:54Z\u0022 title=\u002206/05/2019 10:07  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EJune 5, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by GearsNSuch\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}